('El doctor Valentino Rossi pasa consulta a una Ducati muy enferma.', ' VR 46: "Mi sueÃ±o es el dÃ©cimo tÃ­tulo"', '&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; text-align: left; ">Despu&eacute;s de un a&ntilde;o horrible,tanto en lo personal como en lo profesional, Valentino Rossi no pierde la ilusi&oacute;n de hacerse con su decimo mundial, posiblemente se enfrenta a uno de los retos mas duros,recuperar el trono de Moto gp ante unos guerreros muy j&oacute;venes y con mucha experiencia.</span>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: left; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', Times, serif; ">Valentino conf&iacute;a en reanimar su Ducati y lo hace con menos apoyos de lo normal,la confianza en &eacute;l ya valla siendo menos aunque sus aficionados (la mejor afici&oacute;n) nunca le abandonan,jam&aacute;s puedes dar por perdido a un ganador como Valentino,en ese error callo Andrea Dovicioso: &quot;<em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">No es broma. Hoy d&iacute;a, incluso subido en una moto japonesa, Valentino Rossi no dominar&iacute;a como hace algunos a&ntilde;os</em>&quot; ante tan duras declaraciones el Dios del motociclismo no tardo en contestarle&nbsp;&quot;<em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">Cuando un deportista gana algo importante sale a la luz su verdadero car&aacute;cter. El problema es que &eacute;l no ha ganado</em>&quot;<br />\r\n<img width="0" height="0" align="middle" alt="" src="http://www.hiltonmotors.com.uy/fotos/3c647ad13202ad46f8b62340d3f1d52e_o.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; ">Valentino reconoci&oacute; no haberse divertido durante el 2011, comprendi&oacute; que no solo fue una mala temporada para &eacute;l, si no que tambi&eacute;n para sus seguidores, pese a todo continua con esperanzas y trabajando al m&aacute;ximo para recuperar su lugar.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 3px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; quotes: none; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); ">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; word-wrap: break-word; "><strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">VR 46:</strong>&quot;Espero volver a ser competitivo el pr&oacute;ximo a&ntilde;o. Tenemos muchas cosas que probar en la nueva Ducati. El objetivo es tratar de ser m&aacute;s competitivos desde el principio y luego ver lo que sucede durante la temporada. Espero que la nueva Ducati vaya bien. Hemos trabajado duro y tratamos de encontrar la manera de mejorar la Desmosedici. Tenemos muchas ideas y mucha curiosidad por ver c&oacute;mo va el primer test de Sepang del 31 de enero, porque tendremos una moto muy diferente y la esperanza de ser m&aacute;s competitivos con ella&quot;</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; "><strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">En cada entrevista le cuelan siempre la pregunta sobre su ''''posible'''' retirada.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; ">Genio y figura,Valentino Rossi no tiene pelos en la lengua y no solo dijo que no se plantea para nada retirarse ni a corto ni a largo plazo,si no que admiti&oacute; verse siempre con un mono puesto,ya sea en moto o en coche.Tambien le hizo un gi&ntilde;o al mundial de Superbikes&nbsp;&quot;<em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">No s&eacute; si llegar&eacute; a correr en Superbike, me gustar&iacute;a probarlo alg&uacute;n a&ntilde;o, pero no me disgustar&iacute;a continuar mi carrera deportiva en ese campeonato</em>&quot;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; ">Alg&uacute;n d&iacute;a llegara el final de este maravilloso cuento,Rossi aseguro que cuando eso sucediera no se ve como Director Deportivo,aunque todo depender&iacute;a de los pasos elegidos por su hermano peque&ntilde;o&nbsp;<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">Luca Marini,</strong>entonces Valentino se lo pensar&iacute;a&nbsp;&quot;<em style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: transparent; ">La excepci&oacute;n a la regla podr&iacute;a darse si mi hermano quisiera correr</em>&quot;.</p>\r\n<div id="divIma3wrap" class="insertionAdvancedContent imageEditor centerImaEditor" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; vertical-align: baselin